Nemesis Enforcer/Scattershot/Dark One:




Nemesis Enforcer lifted off into the air, cursing at the new robot.  The tank 
hit him in the leg, sending him spinning, crashing into a wall.

---

Scattershot raised his rifle, a blast knocking through through the wall.  
Raising his comm. unit, slowly getting up, he spoke.  <This is Scattershot, 
requiring assistance in putting down that Soundblurb guy>  Raising his rifle, 
he fired off ten armor piercing rounds, not caring they won't do much, 
autogun fire blazing as well.

---

Dark One recieved Scattershot's call, pulling out his sub-machine gun, and 
two charges.  He ran for the room Scattershot's comm. was eminating from.
